 swapping out heavy sugars and infusing your batter with a premium all-in-one protein blend like TrueFit, you drastically slow down that digestive process. A single quality scoop doesn't just offer clean, grass-fed protein to rebuild muscle; it also delivers essential prebiotic fiber and live probiotics.<\/p><p>When mixed with the natural prebiotic fibers from mashed bananas, this loaf provides a steady release of amino acids for optimal recovery, feeds the good bacteria in your gut, and keeps you feeling full and lean.<\/p>","desktop_width_percent":40,"box_padding":16,"vertical_padding":0,"background_color":"#ffffff","text_color":"#000000","font_size":15,"line_height":1.6,"border_radius":8},"blocks":{}}},"block_order":["ai_gen_block_a26d1da_CR7p3L"],"settings":{}},"blocks_GenXGm":{"type":"_blocks","blocks":{"ai_gen_block_0929f29_ErY4Ui":{"type":"ai_gen_block_0929f29","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/TrueFit_007.jpg","image_max_width":400,"image_aspect_ratio":"16\/9","image_fit":"cover","image_position_x":40,"image_position_y":50,"image_border_radius":0,"caption":"<p><em>TrueFit contains 1 billion CFU probiotics to improve gut health and promote healthy gut microbiome.<\/em><\/p>","caption_font_size":12,"caption_color":"#000000","text_alignment":"center","button_text":"Save 30% Today","button_link":"shopify:\/\/products\/truefit-vanilla","button_font_size":12,"button_font_weight":"400","button_padding_vertical":12,"button_padding_horizontal":24,"button_border_radius":8,"button_border_width":1,"button_bg_color":"#5b3b42","button_text_color":"#f0f0eb","button_border_color":"#5b3b42","button_bg_color_hover":"#000000","button_text_color_hover":"#ffffff","button_border_color_hover":"#000000","alignment":"center","spacing":12,"desktop_width_percent":100},"blocks":{}}},"block_order":["ai_gen_block_0929f29_ErY4Ui"],"settings":{}},"17811140795eab01c8":{"type":"_blocks","settings":{}},"blocks_GnLN4b":{"type":"_blocks","settings":{}},"blocks_qQ9EDE":{"type":"_blocks","blocks":{"ai_gen_block_a26d1da_bYLt8t":{"type":"ai_gen_block_a26d1da","settings":{"text_content":"<p><em><strong>The Recipe: Guilt-Free Protein Chocolate Chip Banana Bread<\/strong><\/em><\/p><p>This recipe brings the fluffy texture of a classic loaf but swaps the unnecessary empty calories for high-performance ingredients.<\/p><p>The Dry Ingredients<\/p><ul><li><strong>1 ½ cups<\/strong> All-Purpose Flour<\/li><li><strong>1 tsp<\/strong> Baking Soda<\/li><li><strong>¾ tsp<\/strong> Baking Powder<\/li><li><strong>¾ tsp<\/strong> Sea Salt<\/li><li><strong>½ tsp<\/strong> Cinnamon<\/li><li><strong>14 grams<\/strong> Zero-Calorie Brown Sugar Sweetener<\/li><li><strong>60 grams<\/strong> TrueFit Vanilla Protein Powder <em>(The secret weapon for 25g of clean protein, fiber, and probiotics per serving)<\/em><\/li><\/ul><p>The Wet Ingredients & Mix-ins<\/p><ul><li><strong>3<\/strong> Overripe Bananas, thoroughly mashed <em>(Packed with prebiotic fiber)<\/em><\/li><li><strong>½ cup<\/strong> Plain Non-Fat Greek Yogurt <em>(For maximum moisture and extra protein)<\/em><\/li><li><strong>½ cup<\/strong> Sugar-Free Maple Syrup<\/li><li><strong>⅓ cup<\/strong> Water<\/li><li><strong>2 tsp<\/strong> Pure Vanilla Extract<\/li><li><strong>64 grams<\/strong> High-Protein Chocolate Chunks or Chips<\/li><\/ul>","desktop_width_percent":40,"box_padding":24,"vertical_padding":0,"background_color":"#ffffff","text_color":"#000000","font_size":15,"line_height":1.6,"border_radius":8},"blocks":{}}},"block_order":["ai_gen_block_a26d1da_bYLt8t"],"settings":{}},"1780499764e29092c3":{"type":"_blocks","blocks":{"ai_gen_block_fababb9_PWKDK8":{"type":"ai_gen_block_fababb9","settings":{"video_file":"shopify:\/\/files\/videos\/RSP Ad May 2026.mov","video_thumbnail":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Screenshot_2026-06-10_at_2.03.51_PM.png","enable_loop":false,"enable_mute":false,"phone_width":280,"phone_color":"#1a1a1a","phone_border_radius":20,"show_notch":true,"screen_padding":10,"screen_border_radius":30,"play_button_size":60,"play_button_color":"#ffffff","play_button_icon_color":"#000000","caption":"<p>TrueFit superfan, Shay Click, breaks down how she makes this delicious, high protein, gut-friendly banana bread.<\/p>","caption_alignment":"center","caption_color":"#000000","caption_size":12,"desktop_width_percent":100},"blocks":{}},"ai_gen_block_0929f29_dnBNzF":{"type":"ai_gen_block_0929f29","disabled":true,"settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/TrueFit_004.jpg","image_max_width":400,"image_aspect_ratio":"16\/9","image_fit":"cover","image_position_x":40,"image_position_y":50,"image_border_radius":0,"caption":"<p><em>TrueFit offers 4-5g of fiber per scoop to help maximize protein absorption.<\/em><\/p>","caption_font_size":12,"caption_color":"#000000","text_alignment":"center","button_text":"Save 30% Today","button_link":"shopify:\/\/products\/truefit-vanilla","button_font_size":12,"button_font_weight":"400","button_padding_vertical":12,"button_padding_horizontal":24,"button_border_radius":16,"button_border_width":0,"button_bg_color":"#5b3b42","button_text_color":"#f0f0eb","button_border_color":"#5b3b42","button_bg_color_hover":"#000000","button_text_color_hover":"#ffffff","button_border_color_hover":"#000000","alignment":"center","spacing":12,"desktop_width_percent":100},"blocks":{}}},"block_order":["ai_gen_block_fababb9_PWKDK8","ai_gen_block_0929f29_dnBNzF"],"settings":{}},"blocks_wDjRHD":{"type":"_blocks","blocks":{"ai_gen_block_a26d1da_7piDGq":{"type":"ai_gen_block_a26d1da","settings":{"text_content":"<p><em><strong>Step-by-Step Baking Instructions<\/strong><\/em><\/p><ol><li><strong>Prep Your Station:<\/strong> Preheat your oven to 350°F (175°C) and lightly spray a standard loaf pan with non-stick cooking spray.<\/li><li><strong>Combine the Dry Base:<\/strong> In a large mixing bowl, whisk together the flour, baking soda, baking powder, sea salt, cinnamon, zero-calorie brown sugar, and your vanilla protein powder.<\/li><li><strong>Add the Liquids:<\/strong> Drop your mashed bananas, Greek yogurt, sugar-free maple syrup, water, and vanilla extract directly into the bowl. Mix gently until the flour entirely disappears. <em>(Pro-tip: Don't over-mix your batter, or the protein powder can make the texture too dense!)<\/em><\/li><li><strong>Fold in the Chocolate:<\/strong> Gently fold in your high-protein chocolate chunks so you get gooey pockets of chocolate in every single bite.<\/li><li><strong>The Pro-Baking Method:<\/strong> Pour the batter into your pan. Bake at 350°F for <strong>40 minutes<\/strong>. At the 40-minute mark, quickly open the oven door and tent a piece of tin foil over the top of the loaf to prevent the crust from over-browning. Bake for an additional <strong>6 minutes<\/strong>.<\/li><li><strong>The Perfect Finish:<\/strong> Take off the tin foil, close the oven door, and immediately turn the oven off. Let the loaf sit inside the residual heat of the closed oven for a final <strong>5 minutes<\/strong> to finish cooking perfectly through the center.<\/li><\/ol>","desktop_width_percent":40,"box_padding":24,"vertical_padding":0,"background_color":"#ffffff","text_color":"#000000","font_size":14,"line_height":1.6,"border_radius":8},"blocks":{}}},"block_order":["ai_gen_block_a26d1da_7piDGq"],"settings":{}},"blocks_NkCnbK":{"type":"_blocks","blocks":{"ai_gen_block_5eabd5d_x77w4x":{"type":"ai_gen_block_5eabd5d","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/ChatGPT_Image_Jun_2_2026_05_36_33_PM.png","aspect_ratio":"16\/9","desktop_width_percent":50,"border_radius":0,"show_overlay":true,"overlay_color":"#000000","overlay_opacity":0.3,"show_content":true,"heading":"","heading_size":48,"heading_color":"#ffffff","text":"","text_size":16,"text_color":"#ffffff","text_alignment":"center","button_label":"Shop now","button_link":"","button_text_size":16,"button_color":"#ffdd00","button_hover_color":"#ffc700","button_text_color":"#000000","button_border_radius":40},"blocks":{}}},"block_order":["ai_gen_block_5eabd5d_